## <a id="reqs"></a> Requirements

To use <%= vars.product_short %> you must:

* Be signed up to the <%= vars.product_short %> Early Adopter Program
* Have a <%= vars.k8s_runtime_full %> Kubernetes cluster configured in OpenID Connect (OIDC).
For more information, see [Grant Cluster Access to a User](https://docs.pivotal.io/pks/manage-cluster-permissions.html#cluster-access-user).
* Have a sandbox environment for testing
* Have a Docker image registry that images can be relocated to

## <a id="limitations"></a> Limitations

### <a id="gen-lim"></a> General Limitations

* This product is in alpha. The structure of the product is subject to change in later versions.
* Pivotal does not provide commercial support for its alpha products.
* This product is intended to be used with any Kubernetes distribution. However, given the number of Kubernetes
vendors, versions, and configurations, not all of them have been tested with <%= vars.product_abbr %>.
* Product upgrades are currently not supported. To test a newer version, delete the previous version first.

